description: Reference libraries for Project Arrhythmia modding
releaseNotes:
# **24.8.1**
## Features
- Added in basic save system for story mode. Expect more features to be added in the future, including traditional save slots.
- **If you have trouble loading into story or getting to story levels try deleting your saves.vgs file in your game's folder or your entire settings folder.**
- Added sex. No I will not elaborate.
- Added in WIP splash page after you complete story mode.
- Swap to async file saving for all save data.
## Fixes
- Fix issue with delayed story assets.
- Fix loading screen getting stuck on errors.
- Fix end screen staying around on restart if < / > is used in the description.
- Minor tweaks and fixes.
## Modder Info
- SaveManager (24.7.-) is now known as SettingsManager.
- CurrentArcadeLevel moved to ArcadeManager.
